data.description: Huge price reduction! Spacious country home with attractive architectural features in a quiet neighborhood! No known restrictions. Enjoy porches, both open and enclosed. Oversized two-car garage. Concrete driveway. Stream. Private well. Master and laundry on the main level. Make it your own! Back on the market after repairs made. At this price- Sold as is.
